sp_scores.title: Exploit the Prison Cage's weakness to fire attacks.

tip_battle.message: Party members trapped by Prison Cage have their HP drained away every turn, kupo! The worst part is, there's no way to break them out! The best thing to do is cast Regen on them to keep them alive until they get out!
tip_battle.title: Prison Cage

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Plant Brain's weakness to fire attacks.
Defeat the Plant Brain without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Plant Brain uses its Pollen ability at the beginning of battle to Blind the entire party, kupo! Either equip accessories that protect against Blindness, or have a character with the Blindna ability ready to go!
tip_battle.title: Plant Brain

dungeons.epilogue: With Blank's assistance, Zidane's party succeeded in rescuing Garnet from Plant Brain. As the forest turned to stone around them, Blank sacrificed himself to help the rest escape the Evil Forest.
dungeons.name: Evil Forest
dungeons.prologue: Garnet has been taken captive, and Zidane, Vivi, and Steiner must make their way through the Evil Forest to find her.

sp_scores.title: Win without the White Mage being KO'd.
Defeat Beatrix without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: It's only a matter of time before Beatrix unleashes her powerful Stock Break ability, hitting the entire party for tons of damage! Use Slow on her to buy as much time as you can, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Beatrix

dungeons.epilogue: In the palace, the party found Queen Brahne, General Beatrix, and the mysterious Kuja. Hearing that the king had taken refuge in Cleyra, the queen left the capital, leaving behind Kuja, who displayed concern about Zidane.
dungeons.name: Burmecia
dungeons.prologue: The black mages have left the capital of Burmecia in ruins. Freya is furious at the destruction, and the party hurries to the palace.

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Masked Man without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: The Masked Man only uses physical attacks, kupo! Abilities like Power Break and Protect will make him much easier to defeat!
tip_battle.title: Masked Man

sp_scores.title: Defeat Steiner without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Steiner only uses physical attacks, kupo! Abilities like Power Break and Protect will take the bite out of his hits!
tip_battle.title: Steiner

sp_scores.title: Defeat Steiner without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Steiner only uses physical attacks, kupo! Abilities like Power Break and Protect will take the bite out of his hits!
tip_battle.title: Steiner, Haagen, and Weimar

sp_scores.title: Defeat Steiner before the bomb self-destructs.
Defeat Steiner and the bomb without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: If the bomb goes off, it will hit the whole party for major damage, kupo! Either bring down Steiner before it blows up, or heal everyone up before it goes kaboom!
tip_battle.title: Steiner & The Bomb

dungeons.epilogue: Zidane went backstage after Garnet, only to have her request her own kidnapping. The Tantalus troupe involved Garnet and Vivi in their performance to escape Steiner, leaving Alexandria aboard the M.S. Prima Vista, but the theater ship was brought down by cannon fire from the castle and crashed in the Evil Forest.
dungeons.name: M.S. Prima Vista
dungeons.prologue: Our story begins with a performance in celebration of Princess Garnet's birthday that brings Zidane, Vivi, and the princess together.

sp_scores.title: Defeat Beatrix without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: It's only a matter of time before Beatrix unleashes her powerful Stock Break ability, hitting the entire party for tons of damage! Use Slow on her to buy as much time as you can, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Beatrix

dungeons.name: Burmecia
dungeons.prologue: The black mages have left the capital of Burmecia in ruins. Freya is furious at the destruction, and the party hurries to the palace.

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Black Waltz 2 without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: When Black Waltz 2's HP gets low, it will counter certain elemental magic attacks by casting a spell of the same element that hits the entire party, kupo! Switch to physical attacks once you get its HP low enough!
tip_battle.title: Black Waltz 2

dungeons.epilogue: Vivi was taken away by a villager in Dali, but when Zidane and Dagger went looking for him, they discovered many other black mages, all identical to their friend. The villagers of Dali were manufacturing black mages for Alexandria. Reunited, the party fought off the assassin Black Waltz 2 and boarded a cargo ship.
dungeons.name: Village of Dali
dungeons.prologue: After escaping pursuit and passing along the slippery paths of the Ice Cavern, Garnet takes the name Dagger to conceal her identity. The party arrives in the small village of Dali.

sp_scores.title: Exploit Gizamaluk's weakness to lightning attacks.
Exploit Gizamaluk's weakness to wind attacks.

tip_battle.message: Gizamaluk counterattacks with Lunge if you hit it with physical attacks! And if you hit it with magic, it will Silence you, kupo! To sidestep all these counterattacks, try hitting it with debuffs first!
tip_battle.title: Gizamaluk

dungeons.epilogue: The party arrived at Gizamaluk's Grotto on their way to Burmecia, seeing the signs of the black mage attack everywhere. With their new companion, Quina, Zidane's party had figured out the system of bells allowing passage through the grotto, when the black mage commanders Zorn and Thorn attacked. Surviving this, the party defeated the insane Gizamaluk and made their way out.
dungeons.name: Gizamaluk's Grotto
dungeons.prologue: In Lindblum, Zidane is reunited with his old friend Freya, and learns that her homeland, Burmecia, is under attack by an army of black mages.
